  p 
    | Refering to the instructions we found at 
    | a(href='https://www.planetnatural.com/pest-problem-solver/houseplant-pests/leafminer-control/') here
    | we crushed the leaf tunnels in order to kill any larvae and removed the heavily infected leaves. From that point forward, the leaf miner issue slowed down. 
  figure.figure
